song.title: Dimension 2012
song.info:
Note from Necros.
"Dimension 2012" - The only song with a drum loop :) This is vaguely dance-ish style with a few interesting chords thrown in... I apologize if some of the samples aren't perfectly looped, they may click slightly but I feel that they were too good to throw away :)
Also used in the 1994 DOS game Iron Seed http://www.mobygames.com/game/dos/iron-seed ???
